WEBVTT

00:07.633 --> 00:10.083
(panting)

00:10.085 --> 00:11.968
(echoing scream)

00:11.970 --> 00:14.855
(echoing): Now, if I have a gun
in my hand and you shoot me,

00:14.857 --> 00:16.506
<i>then you killed me</i>
<i>in self-defense.</i>

00:16.508 --> 00:17.674
(yells)

00:17.676 --> 00:19.926
But what if I don't
have a gun, Detective?

00:19.928 --> 00:21.928
Please don't
let him kill me!

00:21.930 --> 00:23.263
WILDER: <i>But what if</i>
<i>I don't have a gun, Detective?</i>

00:23.265 --> 00:25.682
<i>But what if I don't</i>
<i>have a gun, Detective?</i>

00:25.684 --> 00:27.434
<i>I'm going to be</i>
<i>with you forever.</i>

00:27.436 --> 00:28.969
(gasps)

00:28.971 --> 00:31.405
(panting)

00:32.274 --> 00:33.523
What's up?

00:33.525 --> 00:34.775
Aren't you going to work today?

00:34.777 --> 00:36.660
Yeah.

00:36.662 --> 00:38.495
(panting softly)

00:38.497 --> 00:40.530
You okay, babe?

00:40.532 --> 00:42.532
Yeah. Yeah.

